{"title":"约翰逊靠狗帮忙","authors":["池北偶","苗地"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊靠狗帮忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗  苗地画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵员不够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何妨征狗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分公母，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论肥瘦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多多益善，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大量搜求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗比人强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并蓄兼收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪汪汪汪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能攻能守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士气高些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临阵不会发抖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"供应易些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用啤酒罐头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比较机动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四条腿善于逃走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比较机灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不致被窝里挨揍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一大好处："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦丢了狗命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省却棺材一口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看第一狗兵师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能给约翰逊帮忙否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报道，为兵员短缺所苦的约翰逊政府，加紧征用军犬来“帮助警卫美国在越南的军事基地”。美国国防部决定把派往南越的军犬增加一倍，达到两千只。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}